ror\", \"from\": 3605, \"to\": 3613}, {\"ngram\": \"judgement\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3626}, {\"ngram\": \"a coaching session\", \"from\": 3634, \"to\": 3652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What happened was completely out of character and does not reflect how I train my horses or coach my pupils, however, there is no excuse.\", \"from\": 3655, \"to\": 3793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"character\", \"from\": 3692, \"to\": 3701}, {\"ngram\": \"my horses\", \"from\": 3735, \"to\": 3744}, {\"ngram\": \"my pupils\", \"from\": 3754, \"to\": 3763}, {\"ngram\": \"no excuse\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am deeply ashamed and should have set a better example in that moment.\", \"from\": 3794, \"to\": 3866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better example\", \"from\": 3834, \"to\": 3850}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 3854, \"to\": 3865}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sincerely sorry for my actions and devastated that I have let everyone down, including Team GB, fans and sponsors.\\\"\", \"from\": 3867, \"to\": 3987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3959, \"end\": 3966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9988674632553372, \"rank\": 0.0011338198765835424, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my actions\", \"from\": 3892, \"to\": 3902}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 3934, \"to\": 3942}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 3968, \"to\": 3972}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsors\", \"from\": 3977, \"to\": 3985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics opening ceremony is on Friday while the dressage competition atParis 2024is scheduled to begin on 30 July, at the Chateau de Versailles.\", \"from\": 3989, \"to\": 4138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics opening ceremony\", \"from\": 3989, \"to\": 4018}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 4025,